title: Onkyo Mini Hi-Fi System CSN755 Overview
description:
Buy Onkyo Mini Hi-Fi System CSN755 - http://www.abt.com/product/64833/Onkyo-CSN755.html

Key Features
• Internet Radio and Music Streaming Connectivity via Ethernet (Pandora Rhapsody Slacker™ SIRIUS XM Internet Radio Last fm AUPEO! vTuner)
• Playback of Audio Files Through Local Network and USB (MP3 WMA WMA Lossless FLAC WAV Ogg Vorbis AAC LPCM Apple Lossless DSD)
• Supports Onkyo Remote Apps for iPod touch/iPhone3 and Android Phone
• Plays Audio CD CD-R and CD-RW
• Three-Stage Inverted Darlington Circuitry
• Symmetrical Power Amplifier Circuit Design
• WRAT (Wide Range Amplifier Technology)
• VLSC™ (Vector Linear Shaping Circuitry)
• Phase-Matching Bass Boost
• 192 kHz/24-Bit Audio DAC
• Advanced Music Optimizer for Compressed Digital Music Files
• Front-Panel USB Port for iPod/iPhone or Flash Memory Device
• Compatible with Optional UWF-1 Wireless LAN Adapter and UBT-1 Bluetooth USB Adapter
